ce:section.ce:para:
Three types of diffusion coefficients are considered when considering the process of extraction from plant raw materials:

                           -

internal diffusion coefficient within solid particles;


                           -

coefficient of free molecular diffusion in the boundary layer on the surface of the particle;


                           -

coefficient of convective diffusion in liquid phase around the particle;

